{% liquid
  assign buy_link = section.settings.buy_link
  if buy_link == blank
    assign buy_link = 'https://amzn.to/3PWsBtd'
  endif
%}

<div class="sliger-page">
  <section class="sliger-page-heading">
    <div class="sliger-page-heading__media" aria-hidden="true">
      <img src="{{ 'sliger-cetaphil-editorial.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="736" height="1333" loading="eager">
    </div>
    <div class="sliger-shell">
      <p class="sliger-eyebrow">Privacy Policy</p>
      <h1>Transparent affiliate skincare shopping.</h1>
      <p>
        This page explains how SLIGER handles affiliate links, analytics support,
        and contact actions. Last updated: June 5, 2026.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sliger-section">
    <div class="sliger-shell sliger-grid-2">
      <aside class="sliger-card sliger-value">
        <p class="sliger-eyebrow">Purchase notice</p>
        <h2 class="sliger-title">Every active product button opens Amazon.</h2>
        <p>
          Review the current product page before buying. Final product details,
          price, availability, payment, delivery, returns, and order support are handled by Amazon.
        </p>
        <div class="sliger-hero__actions">
          <a class="sliger-button" href="{{ buy_link }}" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener noreferrer">Featured Amazon link</a>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <div class="sliger-faq-list">
        <article class="sliger-card sliger-value">
          <h3>Affiliate disclosure</h3>
          <p>
            As an Amazon Associate, we earn from qualifying purchases. Some product buttons
            on SLIGER are affiliate links, which means we may earn a commission when you purchase through those links.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="sliger-card sliger-value">
          <h3>Amazon-only purchases</h3>
          <p>
            SLIGER does not provide a cart, checkout, payment gateway, order processing,
            delivery, returns, or customer order support.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="sliger-card sliger-value">
          <h3>Analytics support</h3>
          <p>
            The website can support analytics added through Shopify apps or theme settings.
            Analytics may help measure page views, product clicks, and visitor behavior in aggregate.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="sliger-card sliger-value">
          <h3>Contact information</h3>
          <p>
            When you contact SLIGER through email, WhatsApp, or the Shopify contact form,
            your message is handled through that selected channel.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="sliger-card sliger-value">
          <h3>Skincare information</h3>
          <p>
            Content on SLIGER is for shopping and informational purposes only. It is not medical advice.
            For skin conditions, allergies, irritation, or treatment decisions, consult a qualified dermatologist.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "SLIGER privacy",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "url",
      "id": "buy_link",
      "label": "Featured buy link"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "SLIGER privacy"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
